[thinking] **Considering JUnit core setup**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m thinking about using JUnitCore with nested test methods and whether to use AssertJ's assertThat with static imports in the outer class. The inner static methods seem able to access these imports. Also, should Checkstyle disallow fully qualified names (FQN) for annotations? If it’s strict, I might avoid conflicts by sticking to JUnit4 top-level imports or combining it with Vintage, but I would really prefer not to use FQN.
[thinking] 
